X = load_wn18()
model = TransE(batches_count=1, seed=555, epochs=7, k=50, loss='pairwise',
    loss_params={'margin': 5}, verbose=True, optimizer='adagrad',
    optimizer_params={'lr': 0.1})
model.fit(X['train'], True, {'x_valid': X['valid'][::100], 'criteria':
    'mrr', 'stop_interval': 2, 'burn_in': 1, 'check_interval': 2})
y = model.predict(X['test'][:1])
print(y)
